models.Name: FoundItem

Definition.readme:
# Found Item

This model represents an item that has been found and registered into the system.

Note that *Found* items defer from *Lost* items.

A lost item are registered by the person who lost the item. 

Found items are registered by someone who has seen an unattended item and reports it as having been 'found'.
